---
title: Tre Funghi and Arugula Salad Serves 2 | with Parmesan and Garlic Croutons
description: Inspired by a restaurant fave, this salad highlights crispy mushrooms ON a bed of mixed spinach and arugula. Homemade garlicky croutons and savoury Parmesan complete this delicious appetizer.

